metadata.name: Angry Falcon NFT #1
metadata.description: Welcome to the Angry Falcons community! We are firm believers that luxury is the expression of taste and creative identity so being unique is what counts. That’s why we are providing an exclusive, limited edition 3D NFT of 10,000 Angry Falcon tokens living on the Ethereum blockchain. What makes this special? Each falcon is a 1 of 1 based on a combination of random attributes that will make the collectible unique and provide an image the holder can relate to. That image is one of confidence, strength and aspiration. What really makes this stand out is that this collectible is a utility NFT which is so much more than a one-of-a-kind piece of art: This token is your gateway to the Angry Falcons’ exclusive lifestyle community. This is cutting-edge: This is truly a Lifestyle NFT.
